# 📝 Noteory

Noteory is a simple and secure MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js) stack web app that allows users to **create, read, update, and delete personal notes**.

## 🚀 Features

- User authentication using **JWT**
- Secure notes storage – each user can only access their own notes
- Add, edit, and delete notes in real-time
- Responsive and user-friendly UI
- Backend and frontend deployed on **Vercel**

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

🔗 [Visit Noteory](https://noteory.vercel.app/noteory)

---
## ⚙️ Tech Stack

### 💻 Frontend
- React.js
- React Router
- Tailwind CSS
- Toastify

### 🖥️ Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB (Mongoose)
- JWT Authentication
- Bcrypt (for password hashing)
- CORS

